@startuml
title Viaverse Admin Case / Appeal — State Diagram

[*] --> OPENED
OPENED --> TRIAGE : create
TRIAGE --> ASSIGNED : assign
ASSIGNED --> UNDER_REVIEW : start review
UNDER_REVIEW --> ACTION_APPLIED : apply action
ACTION_APPLIED --> CLOSED : audit + notify
UNDER_REVIEW --> ESCALATED : complex
ESCALATED --> UNDER_REVIEW : return
CLOSED --> APPEAL_OPENED : appeal submitted
APPEAL_OPENED --> APPEAL_REVIEW : assign appeal
APPEAL_REVIEW --> APPEAL_RESOLVED : resolve
APPEAL_RESOLVED --> CLOSED : final close
CLOSED --> [*]

note bottom
Appeal resolution must not be performed by the same admin
when policy requires separation of duties.
end note
@enduml
